snippet.title: DIRE VENGEANCE
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1682030/Dire_Vengeance/

Pandora ventures into the Dark Realm to slay the demons who threaten her world. Collect Soul Orbs to upgrade your abilities and uncover arcane weaponry. Slash your way through frozen wastelands, lava filled chambers, and caverns of putrefying flesh as you slaughter hordes of condemned monstrosities.
